            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "What's wrong, Plachta? Are you thinking about something?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "...Yes, I'm wondering what I could do to become stronger."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x26,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Wow, that sounds like something a warrior would say."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x28,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "I think you're plenty strong already..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "No, that's not true. I at least need the power to annihilate an approaching swarm of dragons in a single attack..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "A-ahaha... Those are some pretty high goals... But I understand the feeling of wanting to get stronger."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "You too...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x32,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Yeah. It would feel really great to take down a big monster in one hit, like... Eyah!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "It would feel great... That's not really the reason, but... W-well, that's fine."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Anyway, I want more strength than I have now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x32,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Strength, huh... Maybe I'll try thinking about it too."
        }
    ]
